|               |               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                 HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(r_regionkey@0, n_regionkey@3)], projection=[l_extendedprice@1, l_discount@2, n_name@3]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                   ProjectionExec: expr=[r_regionkey@0 as r_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
